guardians.model.entities

Class Absence

  • java.lang.Object
    • guardians.model.entities.Absence

  • @Entity
 @ValidAbsenceDates
public class Absence
extends java.lang.Object
    This Entity represents the Absence of a Doctor during a certain period An absence may occur, for example, if the Doctor is sick or in their holidays Absence is a weak entity. Hence, it receives its primary key from the corresponding Doctor There are certain constraints an Absence has to meet to be considered valid. See ValidAbsenceDates
    Author:
    miggoncan
